      <title>拜登表示正在考虑澳大利亚撤销对阿桑奇起诉的请求</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-says-he-is-considering-australia-request-drop-assange-prosecution-2024-04-10/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登周三表示，他正在考虑澳大利亚提出的撤销对维基解密创始人朱利安·阿桑奇的起诉的请求，阿桑奇泄露了大量美国机密文件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/biden-says-he-is-considering-australia-request-drop-assange-prosecution-2024-04-10/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 16:45:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>独家：富士康考虑在管理层改组中轮换首席执行官</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/foxconn-considers-rotating-ceos-management-reshuffle-2024-04-10/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三名知情人士告诉路透社，苹果供应商富士康正在考虑引入轮值首席执行官制度，对其管理结构进行重大改革，旨在培养未来人才。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/foxconn-considers-rotating-ceos-management-reshuffle-2024-04-10/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 16:04:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Meta推出新一代AI芯片</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/meta-debuts-new-generation-ai-chip-2024-04-10/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms 周三公布了有关该公司下一代内部人工智能加速器芯片的详细信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/meta-debuts-new-generation-ai-chip-2024-04-10/</guid>
